#### API Summary

#### Segment
* [GetMySegmentsLegacy](#capi-segment-getmysegmentslegacy) - Returns the segments for the current user - in legacy format (i.e. using the existing, numeric segment ids). Available via cloud-code only.
* [RefreshMySegments](#capi-segment-refreshmysegments) - Refreshes the segments for the current user. Available via cloud-code only.
* [SysGetSegmentList](#capi-segment-sysgetsegmentlist) - Returns a list of all segments with basic meta-data. i.e. does not include the criteria details.
